{"word":"ζῷον","slug":"ζῷον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46488\" key=\"zw=|on\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ζῷον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <sense id=\"n46488.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">living being, animal</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.10</biblScope> </bibl> (of bees), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:551\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">551</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg011.perseus-grc1:443\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">443</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πᾶν ὅ τι περ ἂν μετάσχῃ τοῦ ζῆν ζῷον ἂν λέγοιτο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg031:77b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ti.\">Ti.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">77b</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζῷα</foreign>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φυτά</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg004.perseus-grc1:70d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phd.\">Phd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">70d</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg004.perseus-grc1:110e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">110e</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζ. θαλάττιον, χερσαῖον</foreign>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phld.\">Phld.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.98S.</biblScope> </bibl>; contemptuously, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅπως ἡ χώρα τοῦ τοιούτου ζῴου καθαρὰ γίγνηται</foreign> may be free from this kind of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">animal</tr_> (i.e. beggars), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:936c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">936c</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζ. πονηρόν</foreign>, of women, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1521.tlg002:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Secund.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sent.\">Sent.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n46488.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in art, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">figure, image</tr_>, not necessarily of animals (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζῴδιον</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"><quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">, ζῷον δέ οἱ ἐνῆν, ἀνὴρ ἱππεύς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:88\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.88</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: mostly in pl., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ζῷα ἐς τὴν ἐσθῆτα ἐγγράφειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:203\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.203</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.4</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:124\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">124</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:148\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">148</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:515a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">515a</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζῷα γράψασθαι τὴν ζεῦξιν τοῦ Βοσπόρου</foreign> to have <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pictures</tr_> of the bridging of the Bosporus painted, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:88\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.88</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζωγραφέω</foreign>: <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ζῷα ποιεῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg012:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Per.\">Per.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n46488.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sign</tr_> of the Zodiac, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2583.tlg001:2:166\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Man.\">Man.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.166</biblScope></bibl>.—The word is post-<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, no generic word used for <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">animal</tr_> being found till after the middle of the fifth cent. B.C. (<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ζώϊον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0260.tlg001:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Semon.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13</biblScope></bibl></cit>, whence <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζῷον</foreign> by contraction: <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ι</itype> is found in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.372.42</biblScope></bibl>, al.,<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11(2).161</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">B</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">76</biblScope> </bibl> (Delos, <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B.C.</date>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phld.\">Phld.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.166S.</biblScope></bibl>, and in codd. opt. in the Noun; the <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζωός</foreign> (q.v.) had no <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ι</itype>: for the compds. (exc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζωγλύφος, ζωγράφος</foreign>) decisive evidence is lacking: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζῳάγρια</foreign> with <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ι</itype> was read by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:407\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.407</biblScope></bibl>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}